name: mask7
description:
I've created about 1000 of these images and at least 50 are worth at least second look, this is another one of the better ones. My prompt did not include any mention of flowers, the initial image had the mask facing the other direction and was female instead of neutral to masculine.

These kinds of embellishments are why working with GAN models, whether manipulated by CLIP or diffusion networks or through other means is so interesting for me.
